#

Savory Pork and Celery Stuffed Bell Peppers with French Herb Sauce

$12.99
420 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

none

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freelow-carb

Tags:

gourmetsavorystuffedherb sauce

Description

Juicy bell peppers filled with savory pork and crunchy celery, drizzled with a fragrant French herb sauce for a delightful flavor burst.

Ingredients

  • bell peppers: 4 large
  • ground pork: 1 pound
  • celery: 1 cup, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, diced
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • French herbs (thyme, rosemary, parsley): 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
